LibSBML 5.11.0 API Reference Manuals

LibSBML provides APIs for programming in C, C++, C#, Java, MATLAB, Octave, Perl, Python, and Ruby. The following are the currently-available API manuals, documenting the APIs for a subset of the languages supported by libSBML:

C++ API Reference Manual

C# API Reference Manual

Java API Reference Manual

Python API Reference Manual

MATLAB API Reference Manual

Octave API Reference Manual

We are keenly interested in improving the libSBML documentation. If you find any errors or problems in these manuals, please report them!

Report issue in the documentation

The latest release of libSBML, as well as the documentation and additional information, are always available online on SBML.org:

Go to the libSBML website
